@startuml LoginSequence
actor User
participant View
participant AuthController
participant AccountService
participant ApplicationDbContext
database SQLServer

User -> View: Enter credentials & Click Login
View -> AuthController: POST /Auth/Login
AuthController -> AccountService: AuthenticateAsync(username, password)
AccountService -> ApplicationDbContext: FirstOrDefaultAsync(u => u.Username == username)
ApplicationDbContext -> SQLServer: SELECT * FROM Users WHERE Username = @username
SQLServer --> ApplicationDbContext: User Record (or null)
ApplicationDbContext --> AccountService: User entity (or null)

alt User found
    AccountService -> AccountService: VerifyPassword(password, hash)
    alt Password valid
        AccountService --> AuthController: User entity
        AuthController -> AuthController: Create ClaimsIdentity & Principal
        AuthController -> View: HttpContext.SignInAsync() \nand RedirectToHome()
    else Password invalid
        AccountService --> AuthController: null
        AuthController -> View: Return View with Error "Invalid login"
    end
else User not found
    AccountService --> AuthController: null
    AuthController -> View: Return View with Error "Invalid login"
end
@enduml
